#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:24
msgid "Motivation"
msgstr "動機"

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:27
msgid ""
"Anonymous parameters are a [historic accident](https://github.com/rust-lang/"
"rust/pull/29406#issuecomment-151859611). They cause a number of technical "
"annoyances."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:30
msgid "Surprising pattern syntax in traits"
msgstr ""

