msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:154
msgid "Deprecation strategy"
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:156
msgid "There are two possible ways to deprecate this syntax:"
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:158
msgid "Hard deprecation"
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:160
msgid ""
"One option is to produce a warning for anonymous parameters. This is "
"backwards compatible, but in practice will force crate authors to actively "
"change their code to avoid the warnings, causing code churn."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:164
msgid "Soft deprecation"
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:166
msgid ""
"Another option is to clearly document this syntax as deprecated and add an "
"allow-by-default lint, a clippy lint, and an IntelliJ Rust inspection, but "
"do not produce compiler warnings by default. This will make the update "
"process more gradual, but will delay the benefits of deprecation."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:171
msgid "Automatic transition"
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:173
msgid ""
"Rustfmt and IntelliJ Rust can automatically change anonymous parameters to "
"`_`. However it is better to manually add real names to make it obvious what "
"name is expected on the `impl` side."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:177
msgid "Drawbacks"
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:180
msgid "Hard deprecation will cause code churn."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:182
msgid ""
"Soft deprecation might not be as efficient at removing the syntax from usage."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:184
msgid ""
"The technical issues can not be solved nicely until the deprecation is "
"turned into a hard error."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:187
msgid ""
"It is not clear if it will ever be possible to remove this syntax entirely."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:190
msgid "Alternatives"
msgstr "替代方案"

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:193
msgid "Status quo."
msgstr ""

#: src/1685-deprecate-anonymous-parameters.md:195
msgid "Decide on the precise removal plan prior to deprecation."
msgstr ""

